@node Main "Flecho - Documentation"

                              'Flecho' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Flecho' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} played in a square board where
a number of arrows are pointing in random directions and around
those arrows are various numbers. The idea is to rotate arrows
so the right amount of arrows are pointing to the numbers.
Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

               @{" Install and Play the game " link play}
               @{"   Features of the game    " link features}
               @{"          History          " link histo}
               @{"        Legal stuff        " link legal}
               @{"          Credits          " link credits}


